timeline.message:
Update rabbitmq-component.adoc

Add a troubleshooting entry regarding headers for cases where the same source and destination are the same exchange.
Clean up some typos.
Try to improved some grammar.

timeline.bodyText: This needs to be changed at Javadoc level, otherwise it will be override during the next build and re-generated.
timeline.author: oscerd
